graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18]

    %% External Dependencies - Platform
    Dashboard -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+]
    Dashboard -->|preferred platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.14+]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    Dashboard -->|auth proxy| RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]
    Dashboard -->|metrics queries| Thanos[Thanos Querier]

    %% External Dependencies - Runtime/Libraries
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 20.x]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18.2.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.3.1]
    Dashboard -->|backend framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient["@kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2"]
    Dashboard -->|code editor| Monaco[Monaco Editor 0.50.0]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Core
    Dashboard -->|monitors| OdhOperator[odh-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster/DSCInitialization]
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| NotebookController[notebook-controller<br/>Notebook CRD]
    Dashboard -->|manages| ModelRegOperator[model-registry-operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Model Serving
    Dashboard -->|monitors| KServe[kserve-controller<br/>InferenceService CRD]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| ModelMesh[modelmesh-controller<br/>ServingRuntime CRD]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Feature Components
    Dashboard -.->|optional| Feast[feast-operator<br/>FeatureStore CRD]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| LlamaStack[llama-stack-operator<br/>LlamaStackDistribution CRD]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| Pipelines[kubeflow-pipelines<br/>Pipeline API]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| DistributedWL[distributed-workloads<br/>Training Jobs]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|service mesh integration| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh]
    Dashboard -->|image registry| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry]
    Dashboard -->|routing| Routes[OpenShift Routes/Gateway]

